label: SubordinateSubordinateLocation
comment: A physical location or place which is a subordinate location of a subordinate location.

objectProperties.comment: The unique identifier for this subordinate of a subordinate location, such as a United Nations Location Code (UNLOCODE) or GS1 Global Location Number (GLN).
The code specifying the type of subordinate of a subordinate location.
The name, expressed as text, of this subordinate of a subordinate location.
Physical geographical coordinate information for this subordinate of a subordinate location.

referencedBy.comment: The location subordinate to this subordinate location.
